OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FWhere does Scotland stand  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fwith the attainment gap?   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, As pupils across Scotland receive their
OL,6, results, the BBC has looked at where   
OL,7, the country's attainment gap stands -  
OL,8, and how it has been affected by exams, 
OL,9, the pandemic and government policy.    
OL,11,FIn a nutshell, children from richer    
OL,12,Ffamilies tend to do better at school   
OL,13,Fthan children from poorer families.    
OL,15,FFor the disadvantaged pupil - and in   
OL,16,Fturn for their children - this means a 
OL,17,Flower chance of progressing to further 
OL,18,Feducation and a decent job.            
